                <h1>What to Do When Your Background Check Discrepancies Arise</h1>
                <p>When a background check doesn't match a resume, it raises significant concerns for employers. Discrepancies may indicate potential dishonesty or omissions, impacting hiring decisions. Candidates should ensure their resumes reflect accurate details and be prepared to explain any differences to maintain credibility throughout the hiring process.</p>
